          "component_id": "textual_research",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "desc": "<p><strong>Message</strong></p><p>\"Darn! I lost the bet again, so they forced me to propose to Flora!\"</p><p>\"But those idiots didn't say how I was supposed to propose, so here I am! No one would know who I am, I'm such a genius! Take that, you idiots!\"</p><p>\"Anyway... Flora, I like you. There you go.\"<br><br><strong>Cat's Tail's reply</strong></p><p>Finally, a proposal of love on the message board! We're touched, and wish you the best, no matter who you are.</p><p>By the way, we have the perfect thing for you at Cat's Tail if you ever decide you need the courage to propose face-to-face. With love.</p>",
                "id": "Additional Information8312",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/22/194600931/2e9386550fe8d8b8b9e55fc6c40f213d_5531566944687945321.png",
